Sentinel v0.9.5.102

Summary:
- Add Character ReOCR debug instrumentation instead of changing OCR behavior blindly.
- Emit a dedicated character_reocr_debug_report.json and .xlsx with row, screenshot, crop box, crop strategy, votes, selected character and status per target.
- Add debug metadata to CharacterVerificationEvidence: crop_strategy, text_length, expected_text, observed_text and allowed_chars.
- Keep Operational Truth unchanged; instrumentation is diagnostic only.
- Update docs and version metadata.

Validation:
pytest -q tests/smoke/test_character_reocr_debug_102.py tests/smoke/test_targeted_character_reocr_97.py tests/smoke/test_character_reocr_98.py tests/smoke/test_alignment_guard_100.py
python -m py_compile ground_truth_validator.py parser/targeted_character_reocr.py

Commit command:
git add .
git commit -m "feat(data-guard): instrument character re-ocr debug evidence"

Tag command:
git tag -a v0.9.5.102 -m "v0.9.5.102 Character ReOCR Debug Instrumentation"
